      description: ["Upgraded version of the Entity Detector.", "It does the same as the standard version, with the exceptions of:", "Range can go up to 64 blocks.", "Better entity filters, with blacklist and whitelist.", "Pulse delay can be down to 0.25s.", "", "This Entity Detector does detect Item Entities."],
      icon: "draconicevolution:entity_detector",
