      description: ["The Advanced Energy Cores.", "They're bigger, holds a lot more power and requires Advanced Energy Core Stabilizers. Thats pretty much it", "", "&cNOTE: The Retrieval Task is for the entire ball, which includes the blocks already on the Energy Core. &lDo NOT break the center Energy Core block, or it will lose all its current stored power!"],
