        }
      ],
      description: ["You will need multiple Dragon Hearts you progress through Draconic Evolution.", "But there's only 1 Dragon in The End, so you will have to respawn a new one some times.", "", "You will need 4 End Crystals, each one placed on the middle bedrock at the edges of the Center Portal. This is also the vanilla way.", "This will refresh all the Obsidian pillars, and its End Crytsals and then respawn the dragon"],
