          type: "item",
          item: "draconicevolution:magnet"
        }
      ],
      description: ["I mean, it is a magnet..", "", "The magnet of Draconic Evolution. Doesn't require any power, and will drag in items and XP in an 8 block radius.", "Shift-right click with it to toggle the magnet. Crouching will disable the magnets pull."],
      icon: "draconicevolution:magnet",
