          type: "item",
          item: "draconicevolution:grinder"
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Mob Grinder kills everything in a 7x7x7 infront of it, at ~500 RF per heart damage dealt.", "Everything killed by the Mob Grinder will count as Player Kills, so Player-Only and Experience will drop. The XP Orbs only lasts for 30 seconds to reduce lag.", "", "Can be turned off with a redstone signal", "It is capable of killing Withers, but not Dragons. Damn those dragons.."],
