      tasks: [
        {
          id: "0300000001960000",
          type: "item",
          item: "draconicevolution:draconium_dust",
          count: 32
        }
      ],
      description: ["The first thing you need to get started with Draconic Evolution is you need to find Draconium Ore.", "Those ores are very rare in the Overworld, semi-rare in the Nether and very common in The End.", "Most recipes requires Ingots, but some of them requires Dust. Draconic Evolution does not have a Crusher, so you can not turn Ingots into Dust with only Draconic Evolution", "", "", "I do not recommend playing Draconic Evolution as a standalone tech mod."],
      icon: "draconicevolution:draconium_dust",
