      ],
      description: ["The Flux Capacitor is a portable Battery, that can recharge your armor and tools on the go, so you don't have to return to base as often, or charge as many different things.", "", "It has 3 modes. Charge Armor, Charge Held Items (items in your main/offhand) and Both.", "To change modes, simply Shift Right-Click with the Flux Capacitor.", "This Flux Capacitor does not need to be on your hotbar, but can not be in a bag (and still work)"],
