      ],
      description: ["I hope you grapped that Dragon Egg.", "The Celestial Manipulator can change skies for the cost of power.", "It allows for weather: Sun, Rain and Thunder.", "It allows for day cycle: Sun Rise, Midday, Sun Set, Moon Rise, Midnight, Moon Set, Skip 24 Hours and Stop at current position.", "", "It can activate automatically on Redstone signal, but only for 1 function per Celestial Manipulator.", "So you can set one up to make it permanent day so you don't have to sleep, or you can set it to never rain. How? Sensors."],
