        }
      ],
      description: ["This is the part where I sincerely hope you have some other power generation than Draconic Evolution!", "", "Item Fusion is Draconic Evolutions main crafting method.", "You place the main item in the Fusion Crafting Core, and the fusing items on the Fusion Crafting Injectors.", "Most recipes only requires 4-8 Fusion Injectors, however a few crafting jobs does require 10.", "", "You will need to provide power to the Fusion Crafting Injectors, to do any crafting job. And you need quite a lot of it, which will take ages at 84rf/t.", "After you have placed all the items, click the Start button in the Fusion Crafting Core, or give it a redstone signal.", "Check the Draconic Tables for ranges on the Injectors and Redstone outputs from the Core."],
