      ],
      description: ["This is the chest that can do, pretty much everything, with a whooping 260 inventory slots.", "", "It has a built in 5 slot furnace, that runs on power, at 256rf/t. This furnace has 4 auto-feed modes.", "Off: Well, it's.. off.", "Fill: It will refill what is currently smelting with new items from its inventory.", "Lock: It will always keep 1 item in the smelting slot, reserving it for that ore.", "All: It will smelt every smeltable item that comes into the chest.", "You can put a Core in its Core Slot, to increase efficiency, and it will Ore Double as well if you put a Wyvern or higher Core in it.", "", "Its inventory can be split into different regions, and each of those regions can have their own I/O settings towards the chest, and the furnace.", "Click the I/O Regions button to configure the 6 available color regions.", "", "And it has a crafting table.", "", "If you need more information, the Draconic Tablet should tell you what you need."],
