          item: "draconicevolution:basic_io_crystal",
          count: 2
        }
      ],
      description: ["The wires of Draconic Evolution, comes in 3 Tiers.", "The Energy Relay Crystals are for moving energy around, and can accept many connections", "The Energy I/O Crystals are for Sending and Recieving energy into the Crystal system, and can accept few connections", "For capacity/link stats on the Crystal Tiers, check the Draconic Tablet", "", "To configure the Energy I/O Crystals, you have to shift-right click them with an empty hand.", "The way the Energy I/O Crystals work, you have to configure them like they're an Energy Battery rather than a wire.", "If the Energy I/O Crystal is set to Input, it will take in energy to itself, from what it's connected to", "If the Energy I/O Crystal is set to Output, it will give out energy from itself, to what it's connected to", "", "To link the Energy Crystals to each other, check the quest to the left.", "", "The Basic Tier has a link range of 32 blocks."],
