          type: "item",
          item: "draconicevolution:dislocator_receptacle"
        }
      ],
      description: ["You can also use your Dislocators to create a portal, leading to the Dislocator destination.", "By connecting a Dislocator Receptacle with a frame of Draconic Infused Obsidian, and putting the Dislocator into the Receptacle, it will create a portal.", "", "The requirements for the portal frame, is much like a nether portal - There must not be any holes in the inner frame (so you don't need to fill corners), however it can be any shape you desire, and can be flipped so it lies down.", "", "This portal will teleport any entity that comes in contact with it, like dropped items, players and mobs. It will also teleport Withers that are still charging up, which makes it a good way to move it out of your Wither Spawning contraption, into a Wither Killing Chamber."],
