      description: ["&r&r&1&rThis is Draconic Evolutions ultimate goal - The Draconic Reactor.", "This is a reactor that runs on Awakened Draconium, that lasts a VERY long time (We're talking weeks of RL time on a server here).", "After the setup has been made correctly, you right click the Reactor Energy Injector, or Reactor Stabilizer to open up the GUI.", "", "The Core GUI has 4 lines:", "&lCore Temperature: &r&rHow hot it is. Higher means more RF produces, and higher fuel consumption. This also determines the size of the Reactor ball. If it touches the Reactor Stabilizers, they will explode, and thus, the Reactor will explode.", "&lContainment Field Strength:&r How strong the Shield is. This is what you Inject and draw RF from. If this reaches 0, the Reactor will explode.", "&lEnergy Satuation: &rHow efficient it is, in fuel to RF conversion. The higher the better, although it usually also means lower Core Temperature.", "&lFuel Conversion Level:&r How far it is with burning the current fuel. When this reaches more than ~85%, the reactor will start to produce uncontrollably.", "", "&lFuel (In):&r Takes up to 8 blocks of Awakened Draconium", "&lChaos (Out):&r Produces Chaos Shards as waste", "", "The core fundementals of how the Draconic Reactor works is, you apply RF to create a shield around the around the core reactor where the RF production is happening. The RF produced is then applied to the shield, to make itself stronger. You then draw RF from the shield, and store it.", "", "To start the Reactor, you need to put up to 8 Awakened Draconium Block and click Charge. This will begin to warm up the Reactor. You then need to pump at least 7 million RF into the Reactor Energy Injector for the shield.", "Congratulations, your Reactor is now running, and producing power", "", "I highly recommend playing with this in Creative first, to get a feel for how it works, and how it can go wrong. And also just to see the pretty explosion!", "For an optimal setup, or ComputerCraft script, I advise you to search on Google."],
      icon: "draconicevolution:reactor_core",
      dependencies: ["02000000015E0000", "0200000001760000", "02000000017C0000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "0400000001B70000",
